Dialogue: 2,0:20:36.29,0:20:39.25,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}yokaze ni fukare kangaeru
Dialogue: 2,0:20:36.29,0:20:39.25,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}And as I feel the wind against them, I always think
Dialogue: 2,0:20:39.25,0:20:44.68,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}suki kirai kirai suki kurikaesu
Dialogue: 2,0:20:39.25,0:20:44.68,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Love? Hate? Hate? Love? Over and over
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.85,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}sono hitomi ni utsutteiru no wa
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.85,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}What are you seeing in those eyes of yours?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.73,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}real sore tomo nijigen
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.73,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Reality or something 2-D?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:51.73,0:20:57.31,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}tayasuku kawaii da nante iwanai de yo ne
Dialogue: 2,0:20:51.73,0:20:57.31,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Don't just say I look pretty like it's no big deal to me
Dialogue: 2,0:20:57.31,0:21:03.65,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}ashita mo me wo kosutte ohayou wo itte
Dialogue: 2,0:20:57.31,0:21:03.65,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Tomorrow, you'll rub your eyes and say "good morning"
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.65,0:21:10.54,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}tawai mo nai koto takusan oshiete
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.65,0:21:10.54,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}And talk about all sorts of pointless stuff
Dialogue: 2,0:21:10.54,0:21:17.08,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}sukoshizutsu chikadzuiteku kyori ni
Dialogue: 2,0:21:10.54,0:21:17.08,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}And as we slowly grow closer together
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.08,0:21:23.13,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}doushiyou jibun ja nai mitai da
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.08,0:21:23.13,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}What do I do? What am I usually like?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:23.59,0:21:27.47,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}merry-go-round ga tomaranakute
Dialogue: 2,0:21:23.59,0:21:27.47,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}This merry-go-round just never stops
Dialogue: 2,0:21:27.47,0:21:33.27,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}mawaru mawaru keshiki ga kawatteku
Dialogue: 2,0:21:27.47,0:21:33.27,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Spinning, spinning, the scenery blurs by
Dialogue: 2,0:21:33.27,0:21:36.27,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}colorful na yume wo miru
Dialogue: 2,0:21:33.27,0:21:36.27,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Like a colorful dream
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.27,0:21:40.19,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}dokudoku shite karadajuu wo
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.27,0:21:40.19,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Throb, throb, I can feel them inside
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.90,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}meguru meguru kimochi
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.90,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Going 'round and 'round, these feelings
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.90,0:21:47.95,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}mada kotoba ni dekinakute
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.90,0:21:47.95,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}I still can't put them into words
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.95,0:21:52.37,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\clip(37,5,1280,91)\move(-500,24,45,24,0,200)\blur0.5}hitokoto sore de juubun nanoni
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.95,0:21:52.37,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur0.5}Even though one word would be enough
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.00,0:21:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Je koniec.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.85,0:21:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To je.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.82,0:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tak, aké to bolo?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.64,0:22:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Myslím dosiahnuť skutočný koniec.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Som taká unavená.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.98,0:22:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem dopustiť, aby si z toho mala iba takýto dojem.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.33,0:22:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Už ma nechaj.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.22,0:22:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Počuj, Kato.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.69,0:22:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ak si cítila niečo vďaka tej hre,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,potom by si sa mala pridať.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre, pridám sa.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pridám sa, dobre?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.29,0:22:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tak ma nechaj trochu sa vyspať.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.27,0:22:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Skutočne, teraz?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerob také dôležité rozhodnutie, ktoré by mohlo zmeniť celý tvoj život
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.30,0:22:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,na základe únavy a znudenia.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.58,0:22:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bože, si taký otravný, Aki.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.31,0:22:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stane sa z toho iba nekonečný kruh, kde by sme iba hrali hry každý deň miesto toho, aby sme ich tvorili, však?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.60,0:22:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nehádž ma do toho istého vreca s takými neambicióznymi ľuďmi.
